OL,3,CHeadline gig for musician told she
OL,4,Cwouldn't be able to walk again
OL,6,FA singer-songwriter who was told she
OL,7,Fwould never walk or play the piano
OL,8,Fagain after suffering a stroke aged
OL,9,Fjust 17 has defied odds to headline
OL,10,Fher first gig.
OL,12,FLauren Jean, 21, had a devastating
OL,13,Fblood clot on her brain while on
OL,14,Fholiday with her family in Spain
OL,15,Fcaused by an undiagnosed hole in her
OL,16,Fheart.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
