PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772110991
OL,3,CHeadline gig for musician told she
OL,4,Cwouldn't be able to walk again
OL,6,FWhat are the signs and symptoms of a
OL,7,Fstroke?
OL,9,FThe NHS also lists other symptoms
OL,10,Fwhich also could be present
OL,12,FLauren is also headlining her first
OL,13,Fshow at the Copper Bar, in
OL,14,FManchester's iconic music venue, Band
OL,15,Fon the Wall.
OL,17,F"This is the first time seeing it and
OL,18,Fit's beautiful," she says.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772110991
OL,3,CHeadline gig for musician told she
OL,4,Cwouldn't be able to walk again
OL,6,FShe says she is keen to meet other
OL,7,Fartists and managers during the build
OL,8,Fup to the Brits Awards, held in
OL,9,FManchester for the first time, at the
OL,10,Fend of February.
OL,12,FShe is also hoping to make connections
OL,13,Fto help sign a writer's deal for some
OL,14,Fof her lyrics and music.
OL,16,FLauren became well known as a teenager
OL,17,Fbusking on Manchester's Market Street,
OL,18,Fperforming to crowds in all weather,
OL,19,Fand travelling to other cities across
OL,20,Fthe country.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772110991
OL,3,CHeadline gig for musician told she
OL,4,Cwouldn't be able to walk again
OL,6,FShe credits her first reception
OL,7,Fteacher in Clitheroe for inspiring her
OL,8,Fmusical career.
OL,10,F"Mrs Dee - I used to admire her every
OL,11,Fsingle morning. I wanted to be a piano
OL,12,Fplayer like her," she said.
OL,14,F"Every Tuesday I used to go to her
OL,15,Fhouse. She'd make me a hot Vimto, and
OL,16,Fwe sit behind the piano for two hours."
OL,18,FSpeaking about her music and
OL,19,Finfluences she says her sound is
OL,20,F"emotional".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772110991
OL,3,CHeadline gig for musician told she
OL,4,Cwouldn't be able to walk again
OL,6,F"Music to me is just like. It's like
OL,7,Fmy therapy," she said. "I've even
OL,8,Fwritten a song called therapy."
OL,10,FLauren has produced her own single
OL,11,Freleases and has plans for an EP and
OL,12,Falbum, but said it is tough to make it
OL,13,Fin the music business as an unsigned
OL,14,Fartist.
OL,16,F"It is tough - I've recently just
OL,17,Finvested in new studio equipment
OL,18,Fbecause studios are so expensive, so
OL,19,Fif I can learn to do it myself, great.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772110991
OL,3,CHeadline gig for musician told she
OL,4,Cwouldn't be able to walk again
OL,6,F"Now I can add music producer to the
OL,7,Flist and add in a 'mixer' on to the
OL,8,Flist too."
OL,10,FBut given the challenges she has
OL,11,Falready overcome, Lauren has this
OL,12,Fadvice for that little girl in primary
OL,13,Fschool who practised with Mrs Dee.
OL,15,F"I think if I could tell her to just
OL,16,Fcarry on," she said. "Just keep going.
OL,17,FI haven't seen Mrs Dee in ages.
OL,19,F"I hope she is ok, and would love her
OL,20,Fto come to my gig if she can."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772110991
OL,3,CHeadline gig for musician told she
OL,4,Cwouldn't be able to walk again
OL,6,F"But, yeah, just say keep your head up
OL,7,Fand keep going."
OL,9,FEven stronger than before Lauren Jean
OL,10,Fis a name to remember and will be
OL,11,Fplaying Band on the Wall on 5 March.
OL,13,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
